-- Geithner: In China's interest to move faster on currency
-- 
-- Mon Nov 8, 2010 5:29am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/11/08/us-india-geithner-china-idUSTRE6A71L920101108

 

 NEW DELHI  (Reuters) - Treasury Secretary Timothy Geithner said on Monday that it is in China's interest to move faster on appreciation of its yuan currency. 

 He said the United States will work hard to strengthen its economic relationship with China, and that China is beginning to relax capital controls. (Reporting by  David Lawder ; Editing by  Bryson Hull  and  Tony Munroe )